"Noxious Trap
Traps give "poison" debuff. They become "true" traps which cannot be detected (true invisibility) and therefore destroyed, or time out. If you throw a shroom on to an enemy, it detonates instantly." as someone who used to play / plays a lot of teemo now and then top , i actually find this dope even when exaggerated strongly , instashrooms that pop up off on enemychampions is something that decides kills often top - theres nothing more aggravating as a teemo than to watch them pass by a shroom by a milimeter.

